## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of the issue due to the rapidly changing nature of social media and its impact on society. Additionally, the complexity of measuring the direct impact of social media on domestic terrorism poses challenges in drawing definitive conclusions. Further empirical research is needed to quantify these effects and understand the nuances involved.